### Registro de un nuevo usuario (Sign-up)
POST http://localhost:9999/api/v1/user/signup
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Marco",
  "lastName": "Reynolds",
  "email": "Marco.Reynolds@example.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "role": 2,
  "verification": true,
  "dateJoin": "2024-09-14"
}

